# Global configuration section
#   Values here are used as defaults for any following Channel section that
#   doesn't specify them.
Expunge Both
Create Both

MaildirStore Academie-local
Path ~/email/Maildir-mbsync/Academie/
Trash Trash
SubFolders Verbatim
Inbox ~/email/Maildir-mbsync/Academie/Inbox

IMAPStore Academie-remote
SSLType IMAPS
Host mailin.ac-paris.fr
User jcubizolles
# Fetch password from .authinfo.gpg:
PassCmd "echo ${PASSWORD:-$(gpg --no-tty -qd ~/.authinfo.gpg | sed -n 's,^machine mailin.ac-paris.fr .*password \\([^ ]*\\).*,\\1,p')}"

Channel Academie
Far :Academie-remote:
Near :Academie-local:
Expunge Both
Sync Pull Push
Patterns *

